*html-xml-utils-2.8-r1 (22 Jan 2004)

  22 Jan 2004; Mike Gardiner <obz@gentoo.org> html-xml-utils-2.3-r1.ebuild,
  html-xml-utils-2.3.ebuild, html-xml-utils-2.8-r1.ebuild,
  html-xml-utils-2.8.ebuild:
  Renamed the 'normalize' binary to 'normalize-html' as it conflicts with a
  seperate package. See bug #27399 for more, and thanks to reporter
  <degrenier@easyconnect.fr> for picking this one up

*html-xml-utils-2.8 (17 Jan 2004)

  17 Jan 2004; Mike Gardiner <obz@gentoo.org> html-xml-utils-2.3-r1.ebuild,
